Title: API: fixing bulk-delete endpoints for  host_group, contact_group and service_group
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1612267505
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b6

In the previous version, the bulk-delete endpoint for host_group,
contact_group and service_group returned a 400 error when called.
This werk fixes this behaviour.
